    <item>
      <title>莫迪为全国投票前取消的选举债券辩护</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-15/modi-defends-scrapped-electoral-bonds-ahead-of-national-polls</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总理纳伦德拉·莫迪为通过选举债券筹集政治资金进行了辩护，该债券已被印度最高法院废除，尽管反对党指责莫迪的政党利用这些工具从公司筹集资金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-15/modi-defends-scrapped-electoral-bonds-ahead-of-national-polls</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 15:18:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着支出增加，巴西将淡化 2025 年关键预算目标</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-15/brazil-will-water-down-key-2025-budget-target-as-spending-rises</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴西的 2025 年财政目标将比之前预期的目标不那么雄心勃勃，这可能会让那些渴望看到政府计划控制支出和限制赤字的强烈迹象的投资者感到失望。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-15/brazil-will-water-down-key-2025-budget-target-as-spending-rises</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 14:35:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
